Usage: writeSetLoad [-help] [-direct] [-excludeZeroCap] -file <string>
                    [-includePinCap] [-view <string>] [-wire_load]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-direct            # Refers the ports directly. (bool, optional)
-excludeZeroCap    # Excludes the net which has zero net capacitance.
                   # (bool, optional)
-file <string>     # Output file name. (string, required)
-includePinCap     # Includes the pin capacitance. (bool, optional)
-view <string>     # View name for the output file. (string, optional)
-wire_load         # Mark -wire_load option for port (bool, optional)